These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, coffee
1. the person drinking coffee is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Beverage   | coffee | cola |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  software-developer, librarian
1. the software-developer is on the left or right of the librarian##3
2. the librarian is on the right of the software-developer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Job   | software-developer | librarian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, chess
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | chess | reading |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, rock
1. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of punk##1
2. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | rock | punk |

 #################################

 
